<title><%= title %></title>
<section class="restaurant-hero">
  <img src="/<%= restaurant.image %>" alt="<%= restaurant.name %>" />
  <div class="restaurant-header">
    <h1><%= restaurant.name %></h1>
    <p><span><%= restaurant.area %></span> | <span><%= restaurant.category %></span></p>
    <a class="reserve-btn" href="/restaurant/<%= restaurant.slug %>/reserve">
      Request a Reservation
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="restaurant-details-wrapper">
  <section class="restaurant-description">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
      Nestled in the heart of the city, <%= restaurant.name %> offers a unique culinary experience
      where tradition meets innovation. Known for its exquisite attention to detail, seasonal
      ingredients, and a warm, inviting atmosphere, this restaurant is a haven for food enthusiasts
      seeking an unforgettable dining journey. Whether you're celebrating a special occasion or
      simply indulging in the finest flavors Japan has to offer, <%= restaurant.name %> promises to
      deliver a perfect blend of taste, presentation, and hospitality. Guests can enjoy a carefully
      curated menu that changes with the seasons, ensuring every visit feels fresh and exciting.
      From expertly crafted sushi to signature dishes inspired by local culture, every plate tells a
      story of passion and craftsmanship.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="restaurant-info-grid">
    <div><strong>Open Hours:</strong> 17:00 - 22:00</div>
    <div><strong>Closed on:</strong> Mondays</div>
    <div><strong>Seating Capacity:</strong> 24 seats</div>
    <div><strong>Seat Style:</strong> Counter & Table</div>
    <div><strong>Languages:</strong> Japanese only</div>
    <div><strong>Children:</strong> Allowed</div>
    <div><strong>Vegetarian:</strong> Available</div>
    <div><strong>Celebrations:</strong> Accepted</div>
    <div><strong>Cancellation Policy:</strong> 24 hours in advance</div>
  </section>
</div>

